@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wkqqgt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.cos(tmp + 0.10)) / (wp.abs(v0 + 0.85) * (v1 + 0.94 * v1 + 0.62)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp((v2 + 0.71 / v1 + 0.84)))
    v2 = wp.sin((wp.cos(tmp + 0.83) * (tmp + 0.46 - v0 + 0.30)))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.cos((v2 + 0.42 + v2 + 0.47)))
    data[tid] = v0
